    "description": {
      "zh": "这款弹药装有数十个极其尖锐的钢钉，它们可以高速命中目标，使其毫无反击之力。每发子弹均进行了抛光，因此可以对枪伤创面造成二次伤害，当然，这不会对你的霰弹枪带来副作用。射击范围应当为3-15米。",
      "en": "This 12 gauge round contains dozens of razor sharp steel tacks that blast out at high velocity which virtually guarantees that there will be no response from the perpetrator. Each round is buffed with #12 shot thus creating a double shock to the wound area. Absolutely will not harm your shotgun. To be used no closer than 10 feet and no further than 50 feet."
    },
